folder: Bronx River Avenue & Soundview Avenue, Bronx, NY
original_title: Bronx: Bronx River Avenue - Soundview Avenue
text:
Bronx River Avenue, at the southern end of Soundview Avenue, Clasons Point, showing three views of the bungalow colony on the East River shore.
Views 1, 2: July 29, 1928
View 3: August 5, 1935
P. L. Sperr
